A $90 value!

Includes:

    Powder: Small, domed ultra soft brush head.
    Foundation: Thin tapered brush head in flat paddle shape
    Crease/ Concealer: Narrow, tapered head designed to fit into the crease of the eye area/Narrow, tapered head designed to fit into the small spaces under the eye and around nose
